        # Examples
        ```python
        # Custom print example
        Status('This is a test warning. Be warned!', 'warn')
        Status('Oh no, something has totally failed!', 'fail')
        Status('This is fine. Everything is fine.', 'ok')
        Status('Something happened.')
        Status()
        ```
